column5: Drove to the dock and took a pic.Beautifull day and water is like glass.Normally would be some guys unloading boats there from US but not today or tomorrow.That really sucks.Kinda hit me now that it was supposed to be show time for me to.Miss all traffic.Ussually guys get to go to camps on fridays but hwy 105 is really quite.Hope this ends soon so we can get back to normall.Stay safe.
John get a selfie stick you get in the picture,we can't go to Canada so be nice to at least see a Canadian,specially a good looking rugged outdoorsman like you hahaha,your pal rod
Bringing my photographer along on the next few trips.She gave me a haircut today so that id look prettier.lol.
John seeing the lake like that and the beautiful sky that's pure torture for us looking at that,dam we just can't get there to even make a wake on that glassy water
